Package org.cougaar.planning.ldm

Interface Summary
ClusterServesPlugin ClusterServesPlugin is the API which plugins may use to access agent-level services.
LatePropertyProvider A provider of Asset Properties to the LDM.
LDMPluginServesLDM Plugin side of LDM-Plugin interface.
LDMServesPlugin Plugins primary interface to the LDM.
LogPlan Planning-specify view of the blackboard.
PlanningFactory Factory methods for all LDM objects.
PropertyProvider A provider of Asset Properties to the LDM.
PrototypeProvider A provider of prototype Assets to the LDM.

PrototypeRegistryServiceComponent This component provides the PrototypeRegistryService.
